headline: Zimmer Biomet Announces Quarterly Dividend for Third Quarter of 2025
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH), a global medical technology leader, today announced that its Board of Directors has approved the payment of a quarterly cash dividend to stockholders for the third quarter of 2025. The cash dividend of $0.24 per share is payable on or about October 31, 2025 to stockholders of record as of the close of business on September 30, 2025.
